  "text": "I understand that the logos did not plan for the heating effect that occurs in third in our third density transition into fourth. Is this correct? I and Ra. This is correct except for the condition of free will, which is of course planned by the Logos as it itself is a character of free will. In this climate, an infinity of events or conditions may occur. They can not be as said to be planned by the logos, but can be said to have been freely allowed.",
